displayName: City of Oro's Crystal Warehouse B1

parameters:
Exhausted Worker: Haa... haa... I can't make progress with
my work since I hurt my back...

Fatigued Worker: Could it be that you're here to help...!
Did the director finally give permission?

Fatigued Worker: But are girls like you really okay for
this?
Mage Relm: Hehe, Nora-san is good at simple tasks, you know!

Thief Nora: Yes! I'm good at picking locks and breaking
things!

Fatigued Worker: Hahaha, spare me from breaking things. Once
you're ready, I'll guide you to the warehouse where I want
you to organize things.

Fatigued Worker: Make sure you're fully prepared before
calling out to me.

Fatigued Worker: Alright, I'm counting on you! Crystals are
valuable, so be careful!
Thief Nora: I've successfully completed the task!
Fatigued Worker: Huh, you're already finished!?

Fatigued Worker: You were able to handle that heavy crystal
so easily... You're stronger than you look!

Fatigued Worker: This is a reward for quickly tidying up as
promised.
Thief Nora: Wow, thank you very much!

Fatigued Worker: It would be great if you all could come
every time. You have strength and beauty... You're the best
colleagues.

events.name: クリスタルそうこの整理並列

parameters:
Elderly Worker: There are so many exhausted people, it's as
if their lives are being drained by the crystals.

Oro's Guard: I am in charge of monitoring the workers to
ensure that no crystals are brought into their pockets.
